{"tid":2425592,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣佈連登仔原諒咗班保皇狗同中國豬啦","createTime":"2021-02-27T12:29:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T16:07:57.000Z","uid":158766,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"14544e1e36b5b8d4397efb3c2b0b0dcc620938a7","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"出面開po嘅係PR呀？<br />\n<br />\n死隻中國豬吳孟達就有一村人係度懶感概<br />\n<br />\n遲啲到成龍個仆街死 <br />\n<br />\n又另一村人出黎話佢好有貢獻呀 陪我長大呀 武打巨星呀 做起香港動作片呀 又乜又柒 <br />\n<br />\n「唔好話成龍抵死啦⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「我唔會出聲囉」<br />\n<br />\n「講句RIP算啦」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong>19年班學生係街頭畀人打到爆晒缸<br />\n<br />\n每一單自殺都話死因冇可疑嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n呢班仆街就拍爛手掌話自己係中國人好驕傲</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n藍絲同紅底嘅名人都唔抵死㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n全香港都唔應該屌佢地<br />\n<br />\n坐緊冤獄班前線就要畀懲教狗折磨之餘<br />\n<br />\n仲日撚日畀對家笑同屌<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">對敵人仁慈就係對自己殘忍呀<br />\n<br />\n屌你班悼念撚嘅老母</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyxpoGV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyxpoGV.gif&h=27fc1129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"72b4b5cba520bf266ea695593acf69f48aeee617","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rVOcxFE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrVOcxFE.gif&h=3ca80104&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0e43af1e9e4483c466aa5a2b65f01f2bae5df0","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nA9vjk2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnA9vjk2.jpg&h=32ef6dba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9678515ab0c1f657bf1aa270965164f62b8f298","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NxGajmg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNxGajmg.jpg&h=5b0df52f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a0d5bed229f7808cfb0da47c25941cb2b068cdc4","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oAzjcGR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoAzjcGR.jpg&h=04ca4506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"514049adaee6724f47819f64964a8e5a3cdbfc8a","tid":2425592,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:37:33.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">BLUE LIVES MATTER</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff9223a408d9aac0746b89491f5ff015004c53d","tid":2425592,"uid":293937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:37:52.000Z","msg":"達叔死我真係冇咩感覺<br />\n如果係周星馳死我會傷心"},{"pid":"7997d8939474c3ff4d73ad0f6b88532c5cefe16b","tid":2425592,"uid":293783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:38:10.000Z","msg":"食藍店"},{"pid":"d2ffae1d785e50c3b3822a1edad02a847ad4038f","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:39:36.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>屌你香港人咁撚淋善真係有可能令極權政黨畀個選舉權你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"89ae8879ce02e5cc14538dc83f2e36a3e1df35ef","tid":2425592,"uid":111418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f087b360f02d2773b9a2829b609ad1037d6d81c6","tid":2425592,"uid":385411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:41:08.000Z","msg":"算啦，無謂咁嬲，一早睇清香港人，儲錢移民算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aed015e4591b1e8cd6fb6c2c2cb5c91822b7355","tid":2425592,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:42:21.000Z","msg":"要搞清楚一樣嘢，當民主對極權嘅時候，當民主可以容納反對聲音包括極權思想，而極權唔可以容納民主思想，長久落去只會發生一個結果，所以你其實唔可以咁類比<br />\n<br />\n我會覺得對於任何主動向中共投誠嘅藝人比如楊千嬅，都係應該落得個萬世污名，呢個標準應該係一視同仁，我呢度只係指主動去護旗嗰班，主動去掂政治而且親共嘅人。因為其實你可以選擇隻手不沾政治，好似叮噹配音咁，佢死嘅時候幾乎冇爭議性個個都只會rip 佢。但當你選擇咗掂政治而且仲要親共，自然要面對當下觀眾同日後歷史上嘅評價。呢樣嘢要同只係喺tvb做而冇去選擇掂政治嘅人區分出嚟，因為香港娛樂圈嘅公司唔係太多，唔似台灣有成幾廿個台比你揀去邊間做<br />\n<br />\n論親吳孟達不及2019手足親，始終佢嘅立場係對家一邊，正如如果發生喺抗日戰爭之後有一個係之前親日嘅大名人死咗，喺當時嘅社會亦唔會有咩好評語，當然佢對香港嘅影視貢獻不容否定，但我只可以講即使今日啲人話佢抵死亦屬情有可原<br />\n<br />\n另外，今日有大量第一類五毛從中作梗，只能夠靠大家批判性思考諗嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">1.）</span><span class=\"red\">五毛會扮曬兩家人</span>，一邊係縮沙派，另一邊係鼓動派，然後互相對鬧，兼不斷散播負面情緒，達到分化效果。正如你覺得台灣除咗國民黨之外，民進黨唔會有共諜咩？香港呢邊建制固然係親共，但共產黨亦都唔會傻到一隻人馬都唔會安插喺泛民嗰一邊。我唔係話咁就乜都唔去理乜都唔支持，而係大家都應該要有返個正常批判性思維去諗嘢"},{"pid":"a6237d4f9c11a1ee654c471d27e296671cda1cc2","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ujQa3Sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FujQa3Sm.jpg&h=baaf7bf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"180d30ce3504ea2b6304ff05804219d041703ac4","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LTpnVMz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLTpnVMz.gif&h=1ebcad66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc0ee04201176095c327f5abcb3fafc5dc5d0659","tid":2425592,"uid":158766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"香港人還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n熊家俊先生（25歲） - 15/12/2017<br />\n梁凌杰先生（35歲） - 15/6/2019<br />\n盧曉欣小姐（21歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n鄔幸恩小姐（29歲） - 30/6/2019<br />\n麥小姐（28歲） - 3/7/2019<br />\n梅先生（32歲） - 5/7/2019<br />\n范先生（26歲） - 22/7/2019<br />\nCalvin 郭先生（25歲） - 27/8/2019<br />\n姬如希先生（16歲） - 2/9/2019<br />\n何小姐 (27歲)） - 4/9/2019<br />\n陳彥霖小姐 （15歲） - 19/9/2019(全裸墮海)<br />\n曾穎欣小姐 （26歲